name: Eggs with Legs (Skou)
description:
Oups...what happend there O_o

Looks like the Eggs just half evolved.

They are ... Eggs with Legs!

According to Darwin, get rid of them as fast as you can by smashing them against each other.

Controls:

Start a round by moving the eggs with W/A/S/D 

Reload a level with R

Soundtrack by: Brace
